<doc id="40616" wikidata="Q7193351" url="?curid=40616" title="Pigeon sport">
<text>There are at least four main types of competitive pigeon sport:

* Pigeon racing
* Tumbling
* Highflying
* Tippler (Endurance)

Though not quite a sport, fancy breeds of pigeons are also bred to standards and judged in a competitive fashion. Levi in his book &quot;The Pigeon&quot; describes all aspects of pigeon keeping. For exhibition purposes sport pigeons are sometimes grouped as Flying/Sporting Pigeons.
