* &quot;The Citadel of Lost Ages&quot; (novella; &quot;Thrilling Wonder Stories&quot;, December 1950)

====1951–1955====
* &quot;Black Amazon of Mars&quot; (&quot;Planet Stories&quot;, March 1951), expanded and published in book form as &quot;People of the Talisman&quot;
