==Twin towns – sister cities==

Meissen is twinned with:

* Vitry-sur-Seine, France (1973)
* Arita, Japan (1979)
* Fellbach, Germany (1987)
* Litoměřice, Czech Republic (1996)
* Corfu, Greece (1996)
* Provo, United States (2001)
* Legnica, Poland (2017)
